headerSubtitle.en-US: is a curated community of leaders and influencers that positively impact the world.

headerImageAlt.en-US: An illustration of a ladder going up into a head full of turning gears.

subtitle.en-US: TTU is a weird collection of entrepreneurs, technologists, artists, professors and other misfits with a __unique world view__.

column1.en-US: So what connects our tribe? __Synergy__. The belief that bringing together creative minds from widely varying disciplines largely increases the potential of those involved.

column2.en-US: The world around us is changing rapidly and some challenges we can only tackle when we’re united. TTU facilitates events where wide-ranging bright minds connect personally to __share thoughts, insights, and ideas__.

column3.en-US: TTU is built around the concept of __‘Controlled Chaos’__. We curate and connect high-quality members in our TTU format (control) and observe the surprising and often innovative solutions they come up with (chaos).
